00:02:52.350 --> 00:02:55.200
So our null hypothesis, even
though that their not asking

00:02:56.084 --> 00:02:57.680
that, our null hypothesis would be

00:02:57.680 --> 00:02:59.100
that there's no difference.

00:02:59.100 --> 00:03:03.747
That the mean time, that
the mean difference between

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:10.440
wearing Zeppo's, Zeppo's
and Harpo's, and Harpo's

00:03:12.180 --> 00:03:15.350
