want's to see if Harpo's times

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:30.290
are lower than Zeppo's times.

00:03:30.290 --> 00:03:32.690
So what we would want to see
is if the mean difference,

00:03:32.690 --> 00:03:37.690
so the mean difference of
Zeppo's, Zeppo's minus Harpo's.

00:03:38.878 --> 00:03:41.190
We're trying to find if
we can see if we can have

00:03:41.190 --> 00:03:44.863
evidence to suggest that this
